---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about__inner">
      <div class="about__photo-wrap">
        <img
          src="/images/samurai.webp"
          alt="Matt Ketchum — MKUltraman"
          class="about__photo"
          width="400"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about__content">
        <p class="about__name">Matt Ketchum — MKUltraman</p>
        <p class="about__meta eyebrow">Digital Infrastructure · Tokyo · 10+ Years</p>
        <p class="about__bio">
          I've spent 10 years watching Japanese businesses suffocate under
          their own tool chaos. I've helped 40+ SMEs eliminate redundant
          software, automate workflows that were eating 15+ hours per week,
          and build reporting systems that actually show what's working.
        </p>
        <p class="about__bio">
          I work with a small number of clients at a time. When your systems
          are this broken, depth matters more than scale. Industries: F&B,
          media, professional services, events, retail.
        </p>

        <div class="about__vs">
          <p class="about__vs-title">Why not someone else?</p>
          <div class="about__vs-grid">
            <div class="about__vs-item">
              <span class="about__vs-label">vs. Internal IT</span>
              <span class="about__vs-text">Your IT person maintains what you have. I optimize what you need.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about__vs-item">
              <span class="about__vs-label">vs. Japanese consultancy</span>
              <span class="about__vs-text">Local firms sell you more tools. I eliminate the ones you don't need.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about__vs-item">
              <span class="about__vs-label">vs. Doing nothing</span>
              <span class="about__vs-text">Broken systems compound every month. The audit pays for itself.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/contact" class="about__cta">Get your stack audited &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-64) 0;
  }

  .about__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-48);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about__photo-wrap {
    width: 280px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about__photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
  }

  .about__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .about__meta {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .about__meta::before { display: none; }

  .about__bio {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
  }

  .about__vs {
    margin: var(--space-24) 0;
    padding: var(--space-24);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .about__vs-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .about__vs-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }

  .about__vs-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .about__vs-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
    min-width: 160px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .about__vs-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .about__cta {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .about__cta:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-24);
    }
    .about__vs-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }
    .about__vs-label {
      min-width: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
